# MDX Documentation Standards

## Structure
- Use only "Description," "Usage," and "Preview" sections in MDX files

## Code Examples
- Do not include "import" statements in MDX TypeScript snippets

## Reference Implementation
- Follow colocated feature docs, e.g. `src/shared/TariffAssistant/TariffAssistant/TariffAssistant.mdx` or `src/common/DataList/DataList.mdx`

